author: Ken Meyer
title: Swedish Embassy Shoots Back at Trump Following His Admission About Terror Remarks | Mediaite
text:
Swedish Embassy Shoots Back at Trump Following His Admission About Terror Remarks by Ken Meyer | 7:53 pm, February 19th, 2017 
The Swedish Embassy to America has responded to President Trump ‘s explanation of the supposed terror incident that happened in their country this weekend. 
During his rally on Saturday, Trump’s remarks about Sweden perplexed a lot of observers because no one could identify the specific major incident he was talking about. Trump’s citation of a seemingly-nonexistent terror attack became subject to mockery over the weekend, and the Swedish Embassy demanded an explanation from the government earlier today. 
Now that Trump has confirmed that his remarks were derived from a Fox News report , the Swedish Embassy has announced that they will be having a word with the Trump administration about their immigration policies: We look forward to informing the US administration about Swedish immigration and integration policies. https://t.co/x5G3euOWRh 
— Embassy of Sweden US (@SwedeninUSA) February 19, 2017
